{"tid":1085048,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"不封殺華為 日政府：5G不排除特定國家企業","createTime":"2019-03-31T00:35:15.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-01T23:38:58.000Z","uid":52215,"like":1,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"687a2dd0cfc16903977a25a502aca315f8d9f38d","tid":1085048,"uid":52215,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-31T00:35:15.000Z","msg":"美國企圖在全球封殺華為5G網絡的行動再度受挫。日本政府表示，不會在有關採用5G通訊技術問題上，對特定的國家和企業實施排除。另一方面，華為去年的全球銷售收入首次突破千億美元大關，較前一年大幅增加近兩成。<br />\n<br />\n「日本新聞網」表示，日本內閣官房長官菅義偉在記者會上表示：「關於新一代通訊規格的5G技術，我們不會要求排除特定的國家和企業。」<br />\n<br />\n報道認為，此意味着日本政府將不會禁止中國的華為和中興的設備為日本架構5G網絡。<br />\n<br />\n菅義偉表示：「具體採購哪一家企業的設備是通訊公司自己決定的事。但政府期望在網絡安全領域，能夠採取積極的措施，提高安全水準。」<br />\n<br />\n今年初，日本政府內部一度傳出，政府已經要求各大通訊公司禁止採用中國企業華為的產品。此前，日本軟銀通訊公司透露消息說，該公司在5G技術領域，將會用愛立信等設備來替換華為。中國外交部和商務部為此向日本總務省提出了交涉，指此舉將影響兩會經貿關係。<br />\n<br />\n華為發布2018年年報，其去年在全球營收逾7000億元人民幣（約逾1000億美元），大幅增加19%；淨利潤為593億元人民幣，增幅高逹25%。華為輪值董事長郭平亦在會上表示，「致力做全球最好的網絡聯接，將網絡安全與隱私保護置於最優先地位。」"},{"pid":"d92fb80895cbc41c859de25051ff438910799c8e","tid":1085048,"uid":155095,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-31T00:42:27.000Z","msg":"奧巴馬時代錯失先機<br />\n到特朗普又放過中興"},{"pid":"5285eb2e633c8b5c65e71ea1454586e33cd5a7b4","tid":1085048,"uid":34793,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-31T01:03:52.000Z","msg":"做咩個po咁靜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f931d89f1ff29fbc19d2f75c00125b8f108bade1","tid":1085048,"uid":50386,"like":22,"dislike":0,"score":22,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-31T01:06:24.000Z","msg":"日本新聞網（<a href=\"http://ribenxinwen.COM\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fribenxinwen.COM&d=Sk6y7wLkZ8LsH37jlkaP92%2Fv5hJrJLSiIP9i8i%2FMgDc%3D&h=d4528dc0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">ribenxinwen.COM</a>），是一個由中國記者徐靜波創辦的亞洲通訊社旗下的一個中文新聞網站。網站曾於2001年停辦，後於2008年10月復辦，近年其報導受華文媒體廣泛引用[2]。由於網站名稱帶有「日本」兩字，因此容易被誤認為日語媒體或日本人營運的媒體，但事實上網站是一個中文媒體，也不是由日本人營運"},{"pid":"4f7a99a90d9bbe14b95ce2a2a00d85b369340fa6","tid":1085048,"uid":49693,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"quote":{"pid":"5285eb2e633c8b5c65e71ea1454586e33cd5a7b4","tid":1085048,"uid":34793,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-31T01:03:52.000Z","msg":"做咩個po咁靜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-31T01:16:15.000Z","msg":"支那網打飛機文都要去回咁咪好多連登仔都唔得閒 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n其實日本政府係想講:嗱人哋用愛立信喺電信商問題,我無出過聲架 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/give.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"671a5ac769ccf95f31fdb08329e509c90b879cbd","tid":1085048,"uid":205710,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-31T05:37:42.000Z","msg":"連登仔又贏<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3b036ebe8f1ec9c0f94b3c980dfb21ed7265b03b","tid":1085048,"uid":118988,"like":2,"dislike":6,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-31T05:48:18.000Z","msg":"嘩反了反了，作為美國隻狗都唔聽主人命令"},{"pid":"3f4c160757a76ddff3c685be4fd91d4058d65ab2","tid":1085048,"uid":1086,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-31T05:56:13.000Z","msg":"Japan&rsquo;s Chief Cabinet Secretary Yoshihide Suga told reporters Friday that Tokyo is not calling for specific countries or companies to be excluded from procurement. &ldquo;Ties between Japan and China have returned to a normal path and are beginning to develop further. The government wants to elevate the relationship to a new level through frequent high-level visits,&rdquo; Suga said.<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2019-03-29/china-says-unfair-treatment-of-huawei-could-damage-japan-ties\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bloomberg.com%2Fnews%2Farticles%2F2019-03-29%2Fchina-says-unfair-treatment-of-huawei-could-damage-japan-ties&d=Sk6y7wLkZ8LsH37jlkaP92%2Fv5hJrJLSiIP9i8i%2FMgDc%3D&h=3e4a54d9\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2019-03-29/china-says-unfair-treatment-of-huawei-could-damage-japan-ties</a>"},{"pid":"d32b4a6abed75dd3c4194a59dd97d37616a678bd","tid":1085048,"uid":49693,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"3f4c160757a76ddff3c685be4fd91d4058d65ab2","tid":1085048,"uid":1086,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-31T05:56:13.000Z","msg":"Japan&rsquo;s Chief Cabinet Secretary Yoshihide Suga told reporters Friday that Tokyo is not calling for specific countries or companies to be excluded from procurement. &ldquo;Ties between Japan and China have returned to a normal path and are beginning to develop further. The government wants to elevate the relationship to a new level through frequent high-level visits,&rdquo; Suga said.<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2019-03-29/china-says-unfair-treatment-of-huawei-could-damage-japan-ties\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bloomberg.com%2Fnews%2Farticles%2F2019-03-29%2Fchina-says-unfair-treatment-of-huawei-could-damage-japan-ties&d=Sk6y7wLkZ8LsH37jlkaP92%2Fv5hJrJLSiIP9i8i%2FMgDc%3D&h=3e4a54d9\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2019-03-29/china-says-unfair-treatment-of-huawei-could-damage-japan-ties</a>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-31T20:40:06.000Z","msg":"-<em><span style=\"color: red;\">With assistance by Miao Han</span></em> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"453f74d0b096d376251362b0d6f0bfaab83d520c","tid":1085048,"uid":138177,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-01T11:51:50.000Z","msg":"日本新聞網<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":